reviewText: I enjoyed this Dvd  and found it to very entertaining.
Nice ghost dvd kept me interested.
This movie is awesome I had no clue there were a part 2 which I can't wait to get paid to buy it.if you haven't watched it you should because its worth the cost,AT,AT,AT,

I watch tons of paranormal shows & movies, as they are very intriguing to me.  In my opinion, series like A Haunting, My Haunted House & Paranormal Witness are really well made shows and actually kinda scary.  Both Conjuring movies and all the Paranormal Activity movies were horrifying to me, which is why we watch.  These Most Haunted shows, in my opinion, SUCK!  They are in comparison to the series Ghostly Encounters.  Not scary, nor very interesting.
